## compatible

Specifies a list of strings that identify the device. Strings are from most specific to least specific and allow a driver to match against a family of similar devices.

```dts
/* Qualcomm SM8550 — arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
compatible = "qcom,sm8550";

/* Raspberry Pi 4B — arch/arm64/boot/dts/broadcom/bcm2711-rpi-4-b.dts */
compatible = "raspberrypi,4-model-b", "brcm,bcm2711";
```
